I'm aware of previously submitted request that was incorrectly marked as a duplicate (https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSD-253 was making this same request while https://jira.atlassian.com/browse/JSD-257 was asking for a feature to ONE user to see all their tickets across all projects. THIS request is for MULTIPLE users to see each others request within a project).

I'd be happy to provide more details if necessary.

